      <title>星巴克 CEO 上任四个月赚了 9600 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/starbucks-ceo-made-96-million-in-first-four-months-on-the-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，星巴克公司向新任首席执行官布莱恩·尼科尔支付了四个月约 9600 万美元的薪酬，这是美国企业界最高的薪酬方案之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/starbucks-ceo-made-96-million-in-first-four-months-on-the-job</guid>
